Heat the CRISCO(R) Canola Oil in a large skillet over medium heat. Add the garlic and onions and cook, stirring often until just tender. Do not allow to brown. Stir in the curry powder and cook about 1 minute. Add the cauliflower, broccoli, carrots, salt, and pepper. Cover and cook about 4-5 minutes, until the vegetables are just cooked. Stir in the tomatoes and JIF(R). Cook about 1 minute uncovered.